headline: Integrated Quantum Technologies Appoints Former Equifax Leader Jeremy Samuelson as EVP, Artificial Intelligence and Innovation
summary: Vancouver, British Columbia--(Newsfile Corp. - January 20, 2026) - Integrated Cyber Solutions Inc. (CSE: ICS) (OTCQB: IGCRF) (FSE: Y4G), dba Integrated Quantum Technologies ("Integrated Quantum," or the "Company"), a developer of quantum-ready AI infrastructure for global organizations that handle highly sensitive data, today announced the appointment of Jeremy Samuelson as EVP, Artificial Intelligence and Innovation.Highlights:Integrated Quantum Technologies appoints VEIL Inventor Jeremy...
